  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Life-preserving energy radiates from you in an aura with a 30-foot radius. Until the spell ends, the aura moves with you, centered on you. Each nonhostile creature in the aura (including you) has resistance to necrotic damage, its hit point maximum cannot be reduced, and (in Materia) standing from prone does not provoke attack of opportunity. In addition, a nonhostile, living creature regains 1 hit point when it starts its turn in the aura with 0 hit points.</p><p><strong>At Higher Levels.</strong> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 9th level or higher, grants a duration that does not require concentration.</p>",
